  m_text: "Alice and Constance groan in frustration, the guards won\u2019t budge
    no matter how much they plead their case.\n \r\nTheir best bet is to walk around
    and try to find another way in.  \n\nWith a plan in mind the girls turn their
    backs to the guards and walk back into the forest.\r\n"
