  m_text: 'She plops down in front of a tree and pats the spot beside her. Alice
    takes her place and quickly curls into her sister.


    Constance gives her
    sister a warm smile and takes her hand. She watches as Alice drifts off without
    a care in the world.



'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
